    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the CFD hemolysis model provides sufficient confidence for regulatory submission based on the Monte Carlo UQ results and the three-point validation coverage. The assuranceLevel is declared Medium reflecting the team's judgment that the assessed factors collectively support the hemolysis predictions within acceptable bounds. Gaps in numerical code verification and model form assessment were noted but considered acceptable given the conservative nature of the power-law hemolysis model.",
